<node id="A人員">
  <data key="d0">A人員</data>
  <data key="d1">engineer</data>
  <data key="d2">A人員 is an engineer with a broad range of responsibilities, primarily focused on various maintenance tasks. A人員's duties include managing account inventory, submitting reports, and maintaining records for multiple clients, notably B客戶, I客戶, F客戶, G客戶, and A客戶. This highlights the engineer's versatility and expertise in handling diverse client accounts effectively.

A人員 is notably involved in the entire maintenance process for several key clients. For instance, A人員 has been specifically noted for managing maintenance tasks for B客戶 and F客戶, ensuring that all client needs are met efficiently from initial tasks to final completion. This level of involvement underscores A人員's high level of responsibility and commitment to these areas.

In addition to the aforementioned clients, A人員 has also handled maintenance activities for G客戶 and A客戶. The engineer's role includes general maintenance activities to ensure smooth operations for these clients, further emphasizing the comprehensive nature of their responsibilities. This broad scope of duties demonstrates A人員's ability to manage multiple client accounts effectively, ensuring that all maintenance needs are addressed promptly and efficiently.

A人員 has also been specifically involved in handling maintenance tasks and records for B客戶 and I客戶, as well as maintaining the record for A客戶. This reiterates the engineer's extensive involvement in various aspects of client maintenance, from initial tasks to final completion, ensuring that all client needs are met efficiently.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer involved in handling the maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is the engineer who handled the maintenance for I客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer involved in handling the maintenance issue for A客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer involved in handling the maintenance record for A客戶.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-726c374f489423e007bce76f7810b46e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d</data>
