<node id="Splunk角色能力異常">
  <data key="d0">Splunk角色能力異常</data>
  <data key="d1">issue</data>
  <data key="d2">Splunk角色能力異常refers to an issue where admin role capabilities need to be higher than es_admin_user role, leading to adjustments in permissions.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk角色能力異常refers to an issue where the admin role's capabilities need to be higher than es_admin_user, leading to the removal of certain inheritance options and deletion of index deletion abilities.</data>
