<node id="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d0">World Athletics Federation</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">World Athletics, commonly known as World Athletics, is the global governing body for athletics. It plays a pivotal role in managing various athletic events and competitions, with a particular emphasis on the World Athletics Championships. The federation's responsibilities extend to validating world records across multiple disciplines within the sport of athletics.

The organization ensures fair play and promotes the development of athletics worldwide. Its work includes setting standards for the sport, organizing high-profile championships, and maintaining the integrity and prestige of athletics through record validation. This comprehensive approach helps uphold the sport's reputation and encourages its growth on a global scale.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-726c374f489423e007bce76f7810b46e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d4