  <data key="d1">record</data>
  <data key="d2">Splunk每週onsite refers to the weekly onsite maintenance activities for Splunk, involving various tasks and status updates.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite is a weekly on-site activity involving Splunk, described as part of the maintenance status.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite is a weekly onsite maintenance activity performed by engineers.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite is a weekly onsite activity involving Splunk, described as part of the maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite is a weekly onsite maintenance activity described in the record.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite is a weekly onsite activity related to Splunk, described as part of the maintenance status.</data>
