  <data key="d1">actioncategory</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門is a department involved in account inventory and report submission.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is involved in adjusting user permissions for Splunk and handling related tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is responsible for adjusting user permissions in Splunk and setting capability values for roles.</data>
