  <data key="d1">customer</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 is a customer associated with the maintenance record. The entity C客戶 consistently refers to an individual or organization that has a direct relationship with maintenance activities, as indicated by multiple descriptions emphasizing this association. This suggests that C客戶 plays a crucial role in the context of maintenance records, likely involving service requests, repairs, or other related tasks.

C客戶 is explicitly identified as the customer for whom the maintenance record was created. The repeated references to C客戶 being associated with the maintenance record underscore its significance in this context. This association implies that C客戶 is directly involved in activities such as requesting services, scheduling repairs, or managing other maintenance-related tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the customer associated with the maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the customer associated with a maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is a customer associated with the maintenance record.</data>
