</node>
<node id="系統優化建議">
  <data key="d0">系統優化建議</data>
  <data key="d1">actioncategory</data>
  <data key="d2">系統優化建議 refers to system optimization suggestions. In the context of Splunk_B客戶B部門10月月維護, these suggestions are part of the maintenance record. However, across multiple descriptions, it is consistently noted that there are no system optimization suggestions provided in this particular case. This indicates that no adjustments are needed as everything is normal. The absence of any optimization suggestions implies that the system is functioning optimally and does not require further enhancements or changes at this time.&lt;SEP&gt;系統優化建議refers to system optimization suggestions, which were noted as none in this case.&lt;SEP&gt;系統優化建議refers to the category of system optimization suggestions provided during maintenance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6</data>
