<node id="Maintenance Record">
  <data key="d0">Maintenance Record</data>
  <data key="d1">record</data>
  <data key="d2">The Maintenance Record is a comprehensive document that outlines various aspects of maintenance activities and tasks. It provides detailed information about the actions taken, observations made, and status descriptions related to different systems and services.

For Splunk SIEM, the Maintenance Record specifically documents the details of maintenance performed for C客戶. Similarly, it covers the actions and observations related to the transfer of the Splunk monitoring system and VM service. On 2025/12/12 from 13:30 to 17:30, the Maintenance Record details the activities conducted for A客戶, including Splunk credential renewal and verification of system functionality. Additionally, it records maintenance tasks performed on this date from 09:00 to 18:00.

The document also includes information about maintenance activities carried out by A人員 on Splunk Credit Card Processing for F客戶. Furthermore, the Maintenance Record details the actions taken and status descriptions for E客戶's system. It also covers maintenance activities performed on Splunk SH and provides a record of tasks conducted on 2025/12/16 from 14:00 to 18:40.

Overall, the Maintenance Record serves as an essential tool for tracking and documenting all maintenance-related activities, ensuring that systems are properly maintained and any issues are promptly addressed.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record details the activities and issues related to B客戶's Splunk Indexer queue full problem.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record details the actions taken and issues addressed during the maintenance process for A客戶.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773164208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
