<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (A人員, B客戶) involves A人員 in various aspects of maintenance activities for B客戶. This includes handling maintenance tasks, managing the maintenance record, and overseeing the entire maintenance process. A人員 is responsible for these duties, ensuring that all maintenance activities are carried out efficiently and effectively for B客戶. The consistent involvement of A人員 in these tasks highlights their crucial role in maintaining the operational integrity of B客戶's systems or facilities.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員handled the maintenance for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員handled maintenance tasks for B客戶and completed specific actions such as DEP02連動主機檢查and設定檔備份腳本異常.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is assigned to handle maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is involved in handling the maintenance record for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is handling the maintenance tasks for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer support,engineering support,handling,maintenance,maintenance handling,task assignment,task completion,task handling</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859</data>
