<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (B客戶, C人員) involves a significant role of C人員 in managing various aspects of maintenance for B客戶. C人員 is primarily responsible for handling maintenance tasks, which include performing necessary upkeep and repairs to ensure the smooth operation of B客戶's systems or equipment. Additionally, C人員 is tasked with maintaining detailed records of these maintenance activities. This involves documenting all maintenance tasks performed, ensuring that a comprehensive history of maintenance work is kept for reference and future planning.

C人員's role extends beyond just performing maintenance; they are also responsible for managing the maintenance record for B客戶. This includes updating logs, tracking issues, and ensuring that all maintenance-related data is accurately recorded and easily accessible. As an engineer, C人員 plays a crucial part in maintaining the operational integrity of B客戶's assets by handling both the physical tasks and the administrative aspects of maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handled a maintenance task for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handled maintenance tasks for B客戶alongside A人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is assigned to handle maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is involved in handling the maintenance record for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is also involved in handling the maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is assigned to handle maintenance tasks for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer support,engineering support,handling,maintenance,maintenance handling,task assignment,task completion,task handling</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f</data>
