<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶">
  <data key="d7">19.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between C人員 and E客戶 involves C人員, who is an engineer, handling various maintenance tasks for E客戶. This responsibility includes managing the maintenance of E客戶's Splunk deployment. The specific tasks are documented in records such as the 20251202 Maintenance Record. C人員's role in this context is ongoing, with a focus on ensuring that all necessary maintenance for E客戶 is properly addressed and managed.

C人員 has been assigned to handle these maintenance tasks, which include specific duties outlined in various records. The engineer's responsibilities are comprehensive, covering all aspects of maintenance required by E客戶. This role is crucial for the upkeep and functionality of E客戶's systems, particularly their Splunk deployment.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handled the maintenance task for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is the engineer responsible for handling E客戶's maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is responsible for handling maintenance tasks for E客戶.</data>
